entry.title: Stackoverflow with latest git head
entry.summary: The context is a loop that Bitcoin seems to be stuck in, with the information of each step provided. The first bad commit has been identified as 3793fa09ff920fc720dfad3738f105d2c9563662, and the QT version is 4.6.2. The person providing the information offers to run any other tests if necessary and includes their contact information.
